::Dollen::

He sees them come by some CR chambers.
"Thanks you two."
He gets into one, and starts repair.

::DrillBit:: 
He recieved the message from StarScream.
"We are at DarkFate's base, because ours was destroyed. Go to the old
Predicon cave. Look for evidense of a collapsed tunnel. You'll have to
dig through a little bit. When your in, the tunnel will lead you to a
underground lava chamber. The new base is inside the lava chamber on a
small island. Hope to see you soon."
